snippet.title: Timelake: Time Travel Tactics -- Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
[Timelake] Steam Page --- https://store.steampowered.com/app/3296330
[Timelake] Discord Server --- https://discord.gg/sDZ4mCx3

Timelake: Time Travel Tactics is a strategy game where you plan battles across timelines, plot your way through shifting streets, and risk your dwindling resources in this roguelite strategy game laced with cosmic horror. Slip into a dream where time unravels, the mist hides what’s beyond reach, and all you seek—or fear—awaits in the forgotten city.

Follow this channel for more development news on Timelake
